			<h4>Store Directory</h4>
			<p>This is the store directory screen where users can search for stores, either by typing in a specific store or searching through different categories. Once searching is done, a list of results will be shown. From the results, you can get more information about each store, add the store to your current route, show its location on a map, or even find out what sales they have. Users generally liked the layout of this screen, especially the search bar at the top which was instantly recognizable. However, users had trouble searching stores by category because they did not recognize the drop-down box below the search bar as something that they could change. In future interations, we would make it more obvious, either by putting an outline or creating some separation from the background color.</p>
