			<h4>Facilities and Washrooms</h4>
			<p>Facilities, such as washrooms, help desks, and elevators were important to shoppers, and hence we included them in our app in a separate category outside of stores and food. Users appreciated the ability to find the closest facility. Also, users were able to easily recognize the icons used for the different facilities. However, participants found that it took too many button presses in order to find the closest facility, and that it may be too cumbersome in rushed circumstances. Also, they believed certain items, such as customer service, did not belong in the facilities section.</p>
