			<h4>Map and Routing</h4>
			<p>From the stores directory screen, stores can be added to a route and plotted on the map (as shown). Users can switch between floors of a mall by selecting from a dropdown box near the top of the map (not shown in screenshot). At the bottom of the screen is a quick way of accessing the stores that have already been added to the route. Users were able to spot the stores they added in the route due to the color-coding. Although some users found the route to be helpful in quickly getting to their destination, others found it to be not as useful, and wished they had the ability to turn it off. One future consideration would be to give users the ability to toggle the route on and off the map. Also, the current location indicator icon needs improvement as it was difficult to spot for some users. Some users also mentioned that store logos were more recognizable than having their names.</p>
